self.name: messages.setBotShippingResults
self.description: If you sent an invoice requesting a shipping address and the parameter is_flexible was specified, the bot will receive an updateBotShippingQuery update. Use this method to reply to shipping queries.
self.descriptionExcerpt: If you sent an invoice requesting a shipping address and the parameter is_flexible was specified,...

arguments.name: queryId
arguments.description: Unique identifier for the query to be answered

arguments.name: error
arguments.description: Error message in human readable form that explains why it is impossible to complete the order (e.g. "Sorry, delivery to your desired address is unavailable'). Telegram will display this message to the user.
